### Admin: Activate User and Assign Role (sends email)
POST {{LEI_SEM5_PI_2025_26_3DE_05_HostAddress}}/api/users/activate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_jwt_token}}

{
  "userId": "user-guid-here",
  "role": "SHIPPING_AGENT_REPRESENTATIVE",
  "activate": true
}

### Admin: Get All Users
GET {{LEI_SEM5_PI_2025_26_3DE_05_HostAddress}}/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_jwt_token}}

### Admin: Get User By ID
GET {{LEI_SEM5_PI_2025_26_3DE_05_HostAddress}}/api/users/user-guid-here
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_jwt_token}}


### Approve VVN
POST {{host}}/api/vesselvisitnotifications/{{vvnId}}/approve
X-UserId: 11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111
X-Role: PortAuthorityOfficer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dockCode": "D1",
  "berthFrom": "2025-10-24T08:00:00Z",
  "berthTo": "2025-10-24T16:00:00Z",
  "notes": "Morning window"
}

### Reject VVN
POST {{host}}/api/vesselvisitnotifications/{{vvnId}}/reject
X-UserId: 11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111
X-Role: PortAuthorityOfficer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Missing crew list"
}


